{
  "texts": [
    "Generative AI is revolutionizing breast cancer diagnosis by enhancing the accuracy and efficiency of early detection methods.",
    "Utilizing advanced algorithms, generative AI models can analyze vast amounts of medical data, including mammograms, ultrasounds, and MRI scans, to identify subtle patterns and anomalies that may indicate the presence of cancer.",
    "These models are trained on diverse datasets, enabling them to detect even the most minute changes in breast tissue that might be overlooked by traditional diagnostic techniques.",
    "Moreover, generative AI can assist in predicting the progression of the disease and personalizing treatment plans, leading to improved patient outcomes [1].",
    "This technology speeds up the diagnostic process by reducing false positives and negatives."
  ]
}